title: Christian reacts to 9 Shocking Facts of the Quran (will I finally revert to Islam?)
description: Reading The Quran, as a Christian, I was amazed by the Text itself. However, I am not an Arabic Speaker and therefore I am not able to appreciate the full Beauty of the Quran in it's original Arabic State. Moreover, I do not know about the explanations of certain passages withing the Quran that can be interpreted as Predictions. Todays Video talks about the Star Tariq and shows us how it could be a Pulsar. A star that has been recently discovered.
